text:
#repost @alishasartstudio
„Éª„Éª„Éª
#throughbackthursday The Mystic Forest!

I have had a close connection with nature since school days. I studied at a hill station and was surrounded by serene beauty for 7 years. No doubt my first love in painting comes for landscape art!

This artwork was made for my brother in law who lives in Seattle, 5 years ago. He is like a santa who comes every year with goodies for every family member and as a gesture I wanted to give him something handmade. He loves all shades of blue and loves trekking as well, therefore this painting was apt for him and my sister in law . . .
Please DM üëá me if you wish to get something personalised made as per your liking and taste. .
.
